All,

In light of the CardConnect IPO and their acquisition of Merchant Link (which
should close any day now), our friends at GreatAmerica Leasing brought to my
attention that CardConnect is marketing an "end to end" encryption solution
encompassing the technologies acquired from Merchant Link. As you know from
reviewing our previous agreements, we may have some recourse against
CardConnect for this activity, and GreatAmerica requested we at least make
them whole in the event of a breach.

I've been in touch with Taylor all weekend to discuss our options, which he
believes we have several considering the circumstances.

Thoughts?

- J.R.
